### GET /api/v1/admin/tenants
### Descripción: Listar todos los tenants. Requiere rol Admin o Support.
### Headers requeridos: Authorization: Bearer <token>
### Códigos: 200 OK (lista TenantDto) | 400 { "error" }

# @name getTenants
GET {{BASE_URL}}/api/v1/admin/tenants
Authorization: Bearer {{ACCESS_TOKEN}}

### Response esperado (200):
# [ { "id", "name", "isActive", "createdAtUtc" }, ... ]

### Response error (400):
# { "error": "string" }
